sliding window  i
1.it is mainly two types 
2.this kind of problems mainly involved when there is need of working on the  part of the whole 
3.first type is fixed size and the second one is dynamic type
4.fixed type is based up on the given or chosen type of length in the array or datastructure we are wrokingg
5.second type dynamic window size is changes according to reach the given conditions of the problem



